        %h1 Privacy Policy

        %p Helping Hands Puzzle Piece is committed to protecting your online privacy. We feel it is important for you to know how we handle the information we receive from you via the Internet. This consent contains valuable information about how we manage your customer transaction and personal information.
        Please read this policy carefully.

        %p The terms and conditions of use policy, and the privacy policy, identify what users of Helping Hands Puzzle Piece ("Users") can expect from this site, and what we expect from Users. By accessing any areas of this site, Users are deemed to have accepted the Helping Hands Puzzle Piece terms and conditions of use, and the privacy policy identified throughout Helping Hands Puzzle Piece. Throughout this Agreement, Helping Hands Puzzle Piece is referred to as "We" or "Us."
        %p To purchase products and to gain access to some of our content and services, you'll provide certain personal information. As a customer of Helping Hands Puzzle Piece, you'll provide your name, address, telephone number, billing information and email address. This personal information is stored with a third-party vendor. We regularly share, with your permission, our list of names and addresses with other organizations offering products and services that may be of interest to our customers.
        %p If, at any time, you prefer that we do not share your information, contact us at by contacting customer service at hello@gethelpinghands.com or calling 888-910-4668 or send regular mail to:
        %p
          Helping Hands Puzzle Piece
